Netagio,allows,investors,to,automate,their,trading,of,Bitcoin,British,pounds,or,gold,They,also,accept,US,dollars,and,Euro,After,setting,up,a,verified,account,users,have,access,to,Netagio,s,Authenticated,and,Public,APIs,The,Authenticated,API,allows,investors,to,place,a,trade,view,an,open,order,or,cancel,a,trade,The,Public,API,called,over,unauthenticated,channels,reports,bid,and,ask,prices,for,a,variety,of,trades